snippet.title: The Prince of Persia Arrives in Esperia! | AFK Arena
snippet.description:
Time is on no one's side, except maybe his. The Prince of Persia has joined the roster of AFK Arena as a dimensional hero! 

How will his Dagger of Time and combat prowess help him find out the truth of time and shatter destiny?

For more information, subscribe to our YouTube channel and follow us on our social media platforms:
